HEADWORD: Gala
<hw>Ga"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>gala</ets>
show, pomp, fr. It. <ets>gala</ets> finery, gala; of German origin. See
<er>Gallant</er>.]</ety> <def>Pomp, show, or festivity.</def>
